keepafloatd Licensing Overview
==============================

Copyright (C) 2026 croit GmbH

Open-source and community usage of this repository is provided under the GNU Affero General Public
License, version 3 (`AGPL-3.0-only`).

A separate commercial license is also available from `croit.io`.

If you have executed a written commercial agreement with croit GmbH covering `keepafloatd`, that
agreement governs your use under the commercial option. Otherwise, you may use this repository
under `AGPL-3.0-only`.

External contributions are accepted only after croit GmbH has received either a signed
Contributor License Agreement (`CLA`) or a copyright assignment for the contributed work.
See `CONTRIBUTING.md` for the repository policy.

The full public-license text is shipped in `LICENSES/AGPL-3.0.txt`.
Commercial-license contact and notice information is provided in `LICENSES/COMMERCIAL.md`.

Third-party dependencies remain under their own respective licenses. A current dependency inventory
based on `Cargo.lock` is checked in as `THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md`, and CI enforces the allowed
license families with `cargo deny check licenses`.
